    <div class="story-box">
    <header>
        <h1>What is Gamification ? </h1>
    </header>
   
        <p>Gamification transforms non-game activities into game-like experiences to boost participation and
            productivity.</p>
        <p> Originating in the 20th century with retail rewards programs and competitive factory settings, the term
            “gamification” was coined in 2002.

        

         

            Although its popularity peaked in the early 2010s, gamification remains a valuable tool for enhancing
            engagement and productivity in various sectors.</p>
        <button class="btn btn-custom" onclick="openIt()">Watch and enjoy !</button>
    </div>
   

</section>

    <div class="address-box">
        <h1>Gamification Services</h1>
    </div>
    <section id="services_jumr" class="services">

        <div class="service row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/img/Img_Serv_Geners_Characters-2.webp" alt="service1">
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 service-content">
                <h3>3D Modeling</h3>
                <p>Whimsy Games offers 3D modeling for games in order
                    to assist clients in creating immersive virtual gaming
                    environments. their specialists will pay close attention to
                    every detail in order to produce vibrant and lifelike individuals,
                    objects, and settings.</p>
                <button class="btn btn-custom" onclick="open1()">company website</button>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="service row flex-row-reverse">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/img/gamification-for-events.jpg" alt="Service 2">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 service-content">
                <h3>Events</h3>
                <p>Event gamification can help the audience interact with product or service and increase the overall
                    attention towards the event. Gamification for events is used across all industries, and companies
                    are even creating event apps with gamification to take engagement to a whole new level..</p>
                <button class="btn btn-custom" onclick="open2()">company website</button>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="service row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/img/Gamification-E-learning-copy.jpg" alt="Service 3">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 service-content">
                <h3>E-learning</h3>
                <p>The e-learning industry is serving users with a cost-effective, flexible, and accessible option to
                    acquire quality education. Now with the introduction of gamification, the standard of online
                    education is massively empowering students and educators to fulfill their desired requirements and
                    objectives perfectly.</p>
                <button class="btn btn-custom" onclick="open3()">company website</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% let x = true; let left = ''; %>
        <% if (typeof allservices !== 'undefined') {  %>
            
           
              <% allservices.forEach(function(service) { %>
                <% if(x == true){ x = false; left = 'service row flex-row-reverse' } else{  x = true;  left = ''} %>
                <div class="service row <%= left %>">
               
                        <div class="col-md-6">

                            <img src="<%= service.imageUrl %>" alt="<%= service.serviceName %>">
                          </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 service-content">
                  <h3><%= service.serviceName %></h3>
                  <p><%= service.description %></p>
               
                  
                <button class="btn btn-custom" onclick="location = '<%= service.companyLink %>'">Company Link</button>
                </div>
                </div>
                </li>
              <% }) %>
         
          <% } %>
      

          
